-- Oando, Nigerian Petroleum Company,  Rated `Buy' in New Coverage at RenCap
-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 2010-10-11T06:53:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/oando-nigerian-petroleum-company-rated-buy-in-new-coverage-at-rencap.html
Oando Plc had its recommendation set
at “buy” in new coverage at Renaissance Capital, which
estimates the Nigerian petroleum products company will increase
2011 operating profit and cash flow by 40 percent.  The Lagos-based company’s price estimate was set at 80
naira per share, 34 percent higher than its current price,
analysts including Gbadebo Bammeke wrote in a note to clients
dated today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  